@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vdonav(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.35) - v1))
    v1 = v0
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(tmp + 0.95)) + (wp.abs(v2 + 0.22) / 0.06))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.sin(v2 + 0.81) / (tmp + 0.04 + tmp + 0.60)))
    v1 = ((0.55 - tmp) - (v0 - (v1 + 0.13 / v2 + 0.63)))
    tmp = ((v0 / wp.cos(v2 + 0.57)) * ((v1 + 0.64 - v2 + 0.77) + v2))
    v1 = 0.59
    data[tid] = v0
